cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with object localization using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it proposes improved learning techniques for CNNs. Multimedia (cs.MM) is another possible category as the paper deals with image data. Finally, Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) is a possible category as the paper proposes an optimization technique for CNNs.
